#confirmation{:style=>"display: none;"}
  %p
    - if current_project.allow_default_class
      By joining this class, the teacher #{clazz.teacher.user.first_name} #{clazz.teacher.user.last_name} will be able to see all of your current and future work. If do not want to share your work, but do want to join the class please create a second account and use it to join the class
    - else
      The teacher of this class is #{clazz.teacher.user.first_name} #{clazz.teacher.user.last_name}. Is this the class you want to join?
  %p 
    Click 'Join' to continue registering for this class.
  = form_for(portal_student, :as => :portal_student, :url => { :controller => 'portal/students', :action => 'register' }) do |f|
    = hidden_field_tag "clazz[class_word]", class_word
    = f.submit "Join"
